OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,6,Fsome patchy rain. Slowly brightening
OL,7,Fup with the best of the sunshine on
OL,8,Fthe west coast. Still warm but a bit
OL,9,Fless so than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry with sunny
OL,12,Fthen clear spells on the west coast.
OL,13,FBecoming increasingly cloudy elsewhere
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,15,Fthe odd spot of light drizzle possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,18,Fsome patchy light drizzle in east, but
OL,19,Fbright around the west coast.
OL,20,FBrightening up through the day with
OL,21,Fsunny intervals, very warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
